fields.text: First off, don't panic, that plant is drooping but it is definitely not dead. If it had roots just be patient. Give it light, keep it moist, and at room temperature. If it did not have roots you might get it to root if you put a plastic bag over it to keep the atmosphere round it moist. GoodLuck!
